high_descs: Turn to the left, take a step forward and turn to the sink on the right.
Pick up the knife from the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the wooden table.
Slice the tomato on the wooden table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the wooden table.
Grab a slice of tomato from the wooden table.
Turn to the left and walk across the room then turn right to face the microwave.
Place the tomato slice on the plate in the microwave and then remove the slice.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the tomato slice next to the knife in the right hand side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato slice in the sink

high_descs: Go to the drying rack on the left side of the sink.
Take the yellow handle knife from the drying rack.
Turn around, go to the left side of the kitchen table.
Cut the tomato into slices on the table.
Turn around, go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink basin.
Turn around, go to the left side of the kitchen table.
Take a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn left, go to the black stand with the microwave next to the green door.
Cook the tomato in the microwave, take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn right, go towards the kitchen table, at the kitchen table make a right, go to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward a step, and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife next to the spoon.
Turn right, turn right again and walk forward to the table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn right, turn right again and walk to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink next to the fork.
Turn left, turn left again and move to the table.
Pick up a tomato slice from the table.
Turn left, walk forward and turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato slice next to the apple, close the door, heat up the tomato for seven seconds, open the door and remove the tomato slice.
Turn right, walk to the table, turn right and move to the sink.
Place the tomato slice next to the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Transfer a tomato slice cooked in the microwave to the sink.
